The paper focuses on natural language processing (NLP), which is a subfield of computer science that falls under the cs.CL (Computation and Language) category. The paper also discusses multitask and multilingual modelling, which are topics that are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions lexical analysis, which is a technique used in computer vision (cs.CV) to extract information from images. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CV, in that order.
